{"tid":2107362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［支爆戰線］要求國際派機飛越三峽大壩上空視察 有冇得唸","createTime":"2020-07-13T23:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T01:29:20.000Z","uid":196092,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25749173dcbc0be658c86dd36772207a88b9650e","tid":2107362,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:30:14.000Z","msg":"「出於人道理由, 同埋中共隱瞞防疫信息既前科, 為左拯救長江上下游周邊既民眾, 我地正式要求國際（聯合國？美國？俄羅斯？）派機飛越三峽大壩視察, 將防汛戰情公布天下」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成功左, 就加速支爆 俾世界同国內見到中共既防汛戰係幾咁流<br />\n<br />\n失敗左, 就係一道離間計, 話俾班外國左膠知自己係幾咁虛偽, 垃圾, 平時滿口仁義道德, 幾咁大愛, 到頭黎原來係假既, 一講到做實事拯救蒼生就縮晒沙, 由得班災民自生自滅； 即刻變身成深藍, 小粉紅 怒屌境外勢力置災民生死於不顧, 呼籲愛国愛党既同胞成副身家捐晒上去救災, 唔捐既全部舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85bbf772f8b1aa936932600d9b136c2492a5a1d","tid":2107362,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:31:57.000Z","msg":"On9 支那領空 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b81c3d89b6cbab33e398bb2ab1c05b4ea05964","tid":2107362,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b85bbf772f8b1aa936932600d9b136c2492a5a1d","tid":2107362,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:31:57.000Z","msg":"On9 支那領空 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:36:39.000Z","msg":"人民條命重要定領空權重要？ 佢出個聲明話會全力救災就冇問題  放長雙眼再睇"},{"pid":"8999cde3422b8f6d60f156acd7a8faa23d9c8406","tid":2107362,"uid":47355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:37:41.000Z","msg":"如果真係要睇用人造衛星睇咪得lo&hellip;"},{"pid":"f970e3d1713156474c0fe31ab56d536796be7db3","tid":2107362,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:37:55.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854f456